    • createCineplex

      public boolean createCineplex(int cineplexID, String cineplexName, ArrayList<Cinema> cinemaList)
      Creates the cineplex and save the cineplex into the file, it takes in input cineplex id, name, and an arraylis of cinema. It will use cineplex id to check for any duplicates. If there are, we will return false, indicating that it has failed this prevents duplicates. If there are no duplicates, we will append the cineplexlist by instantiating a new cineplex with cineplexID, name, and arraylist. We will then write these to a file and return true.
      Specified by:
      createCineplex in interface CineplexManager
      Parameters:
      cineplexID - the cineplex ID
      cineplexName - the cineplex name
      cinemaList - the cinema list
      Returns:
      true, if successful
